    "originContent": "## Architecture",
    "translatedContent": "## 架构"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "7egPtIcJ5cPIfAm1+dT3I8Ua6wKfovwoPbSswqTiNMY=",
    "originContent": "The server is based on Boost.Beast, asynchronous (C++20 coroutines)",
    "translatedContent": "服务器基于 Boost.Beast，异步（C++20 协程）"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "tJzHZobEoBlYx+77xbVOM7In9zIPWgv7eYAd+OwgBtA=",
    "originContent": "and single-threaded. It requires C++20 to build. It uses Redis and MySQL for",
    "translatedContent": "且单线程。构建需要 C++20。它使用 Redis 和 MySQL 进行"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "ufCfj3zJB2R9FXf4pUs0RRoTzqJnqpKY5sI99CdJedg=",
    "originContent": "persistence.",
    "translatedContent": "持久化。"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "Os0H/5StjRbvnu3Dq6Rz9FWnMLCitSOSsqJuxbaa3pg=",
    "originContent": "The client is web-based and uses Next.js. It communicates with the server",
    "translatedContent": "客户端是基于网页的，使用 Next.js。它通过 websocket 与服务器"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "UDkTCiYv4aIUNpU7/48vuPnXfjBE8LFSdDPaHxOufiw=",
    "originContent": "using websockets.",
    "translatedContent": "通信。"
  },
